NESTED LOOPS:
*A loop inside the another loop
*the inner loops will excute one time for each iteration of outer loop
*An inner loop within the repating block of outer loop

//outer loop

for(let i=1;i<=3;i++){
document.write(i,"<br>");

for(let j=1;j<=4;j++){
document.write(j," ");
}

document.write("<br>");

